[{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0011","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-2069","title":"联想 FileZ 客户端 跨站脚本代码执行漏洞","description":"联想网盘FileZ客户端存在跨站脚本漏洞。该漏洞源于应用程序未对用户访问的链接进行充分的安全验证与内容过滤，攻击者可构造包含恶意脚本的特制URL。当本地用户访问该恶意链接时，恶意代码将在客户端上下文中执行，可能导致用户数据泄露或远程代码执行。漏洞利用需用户主动点击攻击者提供的链接，成功利用后可进一步获取系统权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2025-2069"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-04-25T16:15:26.020","updated":"2026-06-17T09:06:14.687","remediation":"立即将联想 FileZ 客户端升级至联想官方发布的修复版本（请通过 FileZ 客户端内置更新或联想官网下载最新版）。在无法立即升级时，应避免点击来源不明的链接，并在企业网络出口处启用 Web 过滤与 XSS 防护策略作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.filez.com/securityPolicy/2.html?1744703100","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-2069.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2025/2xxx/CVE-2025-2069.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/94ba69fdac5ced9eb8795ce09aa042cbb168d31b/2025/2xxx/CVE-2025-2069.json","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/e2c3d33b7e2870449a687c9b1cfa4c48990c946b/docs/2025/%E8%81%94%E6%83%B3_%E8%81%94%E6%83%B3%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%98filez-cve-2025-2069-%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C.toml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/SSVC/data/2025/CVE-2025-2069.json","https://github.com/Hashmire/cpeApplicabilityGeneratorPages/blob/4588dccb1f913705444975eb2a5eb79962bf2513/generated_pages/CVE-2025-2069.html","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2025/CVE-2025-20697.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2025-20690.json","https://github.com/youngrichu/frp-freedom/blob/9eae82725ec6cc64950e34e505e7a03b39bbc4f9/FRP%20Bypass%20Methods%20research.md","https://github.com/mengyuqiao/LLM-Cyberteam/blob/acc4763d4f71f272105dcd08ef139cbc385a4976/crawl/extracted_cve_ids.txt","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-2069"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0010","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0010.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-2068","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":11095,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":11115}}","description":"联想网盘 FileZ 客户端存在开放重定向漏洞（CWE-601）。该漏洞源于客户端对外部传入的 URL 校验不严格，未能正确验证重定向目标的合法性。当本地用户在终端上访问攻击者精心构造的恶意链接时，客户端会将其重定向至攻击者控制的外部站点，进而可能诱导用户泄露会话凭证、身份令牌或其他敏感信息。攻击需目标系统本地用户主动点击或访问特制 URL 方可触发，利用门槛较低但需用户交互。该漏洞影响使用存在缺陷版本 FileZ 客户端的联想网盘用户，CVSS 评分为 5.1，危害等级为中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2025-2068"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-04-25T16:15:25.857","updated":"2026-06-17T09:06:14.577","remediation":"建议立即将联想 FileZ 客户端升级至联想官方发布的最新安全版本（参考 Lenovo 安全公告 Lenovo Security Advisory），并在升级前避免点击来历不明的链接、仅通过官方或可信域名访问网盘。企业管理员可在网络出口防火墙/代理层对 FileZ 相关域名的重定向目标做白名单校验，禁止跳转到非可信第三方域名，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.filez.com/securityPolicy/2.html?1744703100","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2025/2xxx/CVE-2025-2068.json","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-20682.md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/94ba69fdac5ced9eb8795ce09aa042cbb168d31b/2025/2xxx/CVE-2025-2068.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2025-2068.md","https://github.com/Hashmire/cpeApplicabilityGeneratorPages/blob/4588dccb1f913705444975eb2a5eb79962bf2513/generated_pages/CVE-2025-2068.html","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3d905f6009ce1a0cb55b6b90198454d955586615/SSVC/data/2025/CVE-2025-2068.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2025/04/GHSA-6mpj-6mgp-p7v6/GHSA-6mpj-6mgp-p7v6.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2025-20684.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a1842787-ca71-472f-9c65-8d32e3f9112a.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2025/CVE-2025-20687.json","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-2068"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0010.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0055","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-32433","title":"Erlang/OTP SSH 预认证远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Erlang/OTP SSH 实现中存在认证绕过漏洞（CWE-306），由于 SSH 协议消息处理存在缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 SSH 服务器发送特制的协议消息触发该漏洞，在无需有效凭据的情况下绕过认证并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 OTP-27.3.3、OTP-26.2.5.11 及 OTP-25.3.2.20 之前的所有版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户立即升级至修复版本或通过防火墙限制 SSH 访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-32433"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-04-16T22:15:14.373","updated":"2026-06-17T09:11:59.137","remediation":"立即升级 Erlang/OTP 至安全版本：OTP-27.3.3、OTP-26.2.5.11 或 OTP-25.3.2.20。如无法立即打补丁，可在防火墙或网络层面禁用 SSH 服务对外暴露，仅允许受信 IP 访问 22 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/erlang/otp/commit/0fcd9c56524b28615e8ece65fc0c3f66ef6e4c12","https://github.com/erlang/otp/commit/6eef04130afc8b0ccb63c9a0d8650209cf54892f","https://github.com/erlang/otp/commit/b1924d37fd83c070055beb115d5d6a6a9490b891","https://github.com/erlang/otp/security/advisories/GHSA-37cp-fgq5-7wc2","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/04/16/2","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/04/18/1","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/04/18/2","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/04/18/6","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/04/19/1","https://lists.debian.org/debian-lts-announce/2025/04/msg00028.html","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20250425-0001/","https://github.com/ProDefense/CVE-2025-32433/blob/main/CVE-2025-32433.py","https://sec.cloudapps.cisco.com/security/center/content/CiscoSecurityAdvisory/cisco-sa-erlang-otp-ssh-xyZZy","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-32433","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/code/cves/2025/CVE-2025-32433.yaml","https://github.com/ODST-Forge/CVE-2025-32433_PoC","https://github.com/ProDefense/CVE-2025-32433","https://github.com/omer-efe-curkus/CVE-2025-32433-Erlang-OTP-SSH-RCE-PoC","https://github.com/NiteeshPujari/CVE-2025-32433-PoC","https://github.com/TeneBrae93/CVE-2025-3243","https://github.com/0xPThree/cve-2025-32433","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-32433"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0055.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0009","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-1974","title":"Kubernetes ingress-nginx 准入控制器远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Kubernetes 的 ingress-nginx 准入控制器（Validating Admission Webhook）存在远程代码执行漏洞。在特定条件下，位于 Pod 网络内且无需身份认证的攻击者，可通过向准入控制器暴露的接口发送特制的 AdmissionReview 请求，利用控制器配置校验逻辑中的缺陷注入并执行任意代码，从而在 ingress-nginx 控制器进程上下文中实现远程代码执行。由于默认安装中该控制器可访问集群内全部 Secret，攻击者可借此读取并泄露这些敏感凭据，造成严重的信息泄露与权限提升风险。该漏洞影响未修复的 ingress-nginx 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8（严重）。攻击前提是攻击者能够访问集群的 Pod 网络（如已突破边界进入内部网络或存在暴露的入口）。官方建议升级至 1.12.1 及以上或 1.11.5 及以上版本修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-1974"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-03-25T00:15:14.753","updated":"2026-06-17T08:40:27.847","remediation":"立即将 ingress-nginx 升级至 1.11.5 或 1.12.1 及以上版本（1.10.x 及更早版本无修复需整体升级）。若无法立即升级，应在网络层面限制对准入 Webhook 服务（默认 8443 端口，ValidatingWebhookConfiguration 指向的 Service）的访问，仅允许 kube-apiserver 来源 IP 访问，禁止 Pod 网络或未授权主机直连；同时通过 NetworkPolicy 或防火墙隔离 ingress-nginx 控制器 Pod 的网络，并收紧其 ServiceAccount 权限，避免控制器读取集群内全部 Secret 造成横向泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/131009","https://github.com/B1ack4sh/Blackash-CVE-2025-1974","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20250328-0008/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52475","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52338","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-1974.yaml","https://github.com/lufeirider/IngressNightmare-PoC","https://github.com/m-q-t/ingressnightmare-detection-poc","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-1974.md","https://github.com/vulhub/vulhub/blob/f7944fe38a3988ee533761e6cdb5e68d67eefff2/ingress-nginx/CVE-2025-1974/README.md","https://github.com/kubernetes/website/blob/2582ebe04be71406110a3960a6d16f991a89921d/content/ja/blog/_posts/2025/ingress-nginx-cve-2025-1974.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-1974.yaml","https://github.com/Threekiii/Awesome-POC/blob/0f9e22b660cb1ea12c1c3668f9128d93e08da412/%E4%BA%91%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/Kubernetes%20Ingress-nginx%20admission%20%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20CVE-2025-1974.md","https://github.com/yandex-cloud/docs/blob/47ef534f5e9072b4d738c6292d74938e29bac8d9/ru/_includes/security/security-bulletins/cve-2025-1974.md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/94ba69fdac5ced9eb8795ce09aa042cbb168d31b/2025/1xxx/CVE-2025-1974.json","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-04/Kubernetes%20CVE-2025-1974%20RCE.md","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/5cf36cd0d4ae46fc3e8539fa2825c78bb5f257c2/data/2025/CVE-2025-1974-zwxxb_CVE-2025-1974.md","https://github.com/zan8in/afrog/blob/9f792687ed156d63344016f8bf658946079fb494/pocs/afrog-pocs/CVE/2025/CVE-2025-1974.yaml","https://github.com/hakaioffsec/IngressNightmare-PoC","https://github.com/Esonhugh/ingressNightmare-CVE-2025-1974-exps","https://github.com/sandumjacob/IngressNightmare-POCs","https://github.com/yoshino-s/CVE-2025-1974","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-1974"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0009.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2025/EXP-AVE-2025-0009.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0015","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-29927","title":"Vercel Next.js 中间件认证绕过漏洞","description":"Next.js 中间件存在认证绕过漏洞（CWE-285/863），攻击者通过在请求中构造恶意的 `x-middleware-subrequest` 请求头，可绕过中间件中的权限检查逻辑，直接访问本应受保护的内部路由。该漏洞影响 Next.js 全系版本（1.11.4 至 12.3.5/13.5.9/14.2.25/15.2.3 之前版本），所有依赖中间件进行鉴权的 Next.js 应用均受影响。CVSS 评分 9.1，危害等级严重。修复方式为升级至安全版本或在 Web 服务器层（如 WAF/Nginx）过滤 `x-middleware-subrequest` 请求头。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.1,"aliases":["CVE-2025-29927"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-03-21T15:15:42.660","updated":"2026-06-17T09:05:53.640","remediation":"升级到 Next.js 12.3.5+ / 13.5.9+ / 14.2.25+ / 15.2.3+ 或更高版本；如无法立即升级，在 Nginx/Apache/WAF 层配置规则拦截并删除外部请求中的 `x-middleware-subrequest` 请求头。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/vercel/next.js/commit/52a078da3884efe6501613c7834a3d02a91676d2","https://github.com/vercel/next.js/commit/5fd3ae8f8542677c6294f32d18022731eab6fe48","https://github.com/vercel/next.js/releases/tag/v12.3.5","https://github.com/vercel/next.js/releases/tag/v13.5.9","https://github.com/vercel/next.js/security/advisories/GHSA-f82v-jwr5-mffw","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/03/23/3","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/03/23/4","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20250328-0002/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52124","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-29927.yaml","https://github.com/Nayekah/Next.js-Proof-of-Concept","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-29927.md","https://github.com/nu11secur1ty/CVE-mitre/blob/ac449b44513bd2f0f30db8cbb4c005f5fa38861e/2025/CVE-2025-29927/README.MD","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-29927/README.md","https://github.com/AC-UVC/ARL-ADD-POC/blob/6c052f1c7c726184e0c6325dcf3593f358af7b66/poc/CVE-2025-29927.py","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/2af0d4e6821c2bba628b60025f4ebdb092ca487e/references/CVE-2025-29927-2025-06-07-1805","https://github.com/moyshik7/vul-detector/blob/a5de9b36f7e5bbb96f345b67a2ed54c204298eeb/cves/CVE-2025-29927.js","https://github.com/Oyst3r1ng/CVE-2025-29927/blob/ce976387acd35f5c6a07783f8531890c3bcd97e7/Poc_CVE-2025-29927.py","https://github.com/ARESHAmohanad/rooms/blob/603aa5bc9064039eefc3af86d1baefb7ba8dfdf1/next.js%20cve-2025-29927.txt","https://github.com/coreruleset/coreruleset/blob/3cfcb53d9b64f662d864c10bc7a8c2c0a99fe2ea/CHANGES.md","https://github.com/narwalsguy/CVE-and-vuln-fixes/blob/9daa242594c7562cae728afea291a208ddda13c1/CVE-2025-29927%20Next.js","https://github.com/aydinnyunus/CVE-2025-29927","https://github.com/AnonKryptiQuz/NextSploit","https://github.com/websecnl/CVE-2025-29927-PoC-Exploit","https://github.com/6mile/nextjs-CVE-2025-29927","https://github.com/azu/nextjs-cve-2025-29927-poc","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-29927"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0033","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0033.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-24813","title":"Apache Tomcat 默认Servlet路径等价远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Apache Tomcat 默认 Servlet 存在路径等价漏洞（内部点号），当启用写入权限且支持部分 PUT 请求时，未授权攻击者可通过特制的部分 PUT 请求利用路径等价绕过安全检查，导致安全敏感文件泄露或向文件中注入恶意内容。若应用同时使用基于文件的会话持久化且存在反序列化利用库，攻击者可进一步实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Apache Tomcat 11.0.0-M1 至 11.0.2、10.1.0-M1 至 10.1.34、9.0.0.M1 至 9.0.98 及 8.5.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。建议升级至 11.0.3、10.1.35 或 9.0.99 版本修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-24813"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-03-10T17:15:35.067","updated":"2026-06-17T08:59:39.593","remediation":"升级 Apache Tomcat 至 11.0.3 / 10.1.35 / 9.0.99 或更高版本。如无法立即升级，确保 Default Servlet 的 writable 配置为 false（默认关闭），禁用 partial PUT（设置 allowPartialPut=\"false\"），并避免使用文件会话持久化存储到默认路径，同时移除应用中可能被反序列化利用的类库（如 commons-collections 等）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://lists.apache.org/thread/j5fkjv2k477os90nczf2v9l61fb0kkgq","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/03/10/5","https://lists.debian.org/debian-lts-announce/2025/04/msg00003.html","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20250321-0001/","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-24813-detect-apache-tomcat-rce","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-24813-mitigate-apache-tomcat-rce","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-24813-tomcat-detect-vulnerability","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-24813-tomcat-mitigation-vulnerability","https://github.com/absholi7ly/POC-CVE-2025-24813/blob/main/README.md","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-24813","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52134","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-24813.yaml","https://github.com/Makavellik/POC-CVE-2025-24813-Apache-Tomcat-Remote-Code-Execution","https://github.com/absholi7ly/POC-CVE-2025-24813","https://github.com/iSee857/CVE-2025-24813-PoC","https://github.com/drcrypterdotru/Apache-GOExploiter","https://github.com/mbanyamer/Apache-Tomcat---Remote-Code-Execution-via-Session-Deserialization-CVE-2025-24813-","https://github.com/charis3306/CVE-2025-24813","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-24813"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0033.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0022","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-24016","title":"Wazuh Wazuh服务器反序列化远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Wazuh 4.4.0 至 4.9.0 版本中存在不安全反序列化漏洞（CWE-502）。攻击者通过 API 向 DistributedAPI 请求/响应注入恶意字典，利用 `as_wazuh_object` 函数在处理 `__unhandled_exc__` 时执行任意 Python 代码，导致远程代码执行。任何具备 API 访问权限的用户（包括被攻破的仪表盘、集群内 Wazuh 服务器，特定配置下甚至被攻破的 Agent）均可触发。CVSS 9.9，危害严重。厂商已在 4.9.1 版本中修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.9,"aliases":["CVE-2025-24016"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-02-10T20:15:42.540","updated":"2026-06-17T08:57:53.677","remediation":"立即升级 Wazuh 服务器至 v4.9.1 或更高版本，该版本在 `framework/wazuh/core/cluster/common.py` 中修复了 `as_wazuh_object` 反序列化函数对不可信输入的校验缺陷。在升级前，可在 Wazuh  dashboard 和集群节点间启用严格 API 访问控制（限制 `security/user/authenticate/run_as` 端点的来源 IP），并隔离受损 agent 避免其触发 DAPI 请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/wazuh/wazuh/security/advisories/GHSA-hcrc-79hj-m3qh","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-24016","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-24016.yaml","https://github.com/celsius026/poc_CVE-2025-24016","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-24016.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/c2672e36893bd220d6f65c955e260796d11ed64b/2025/CVE-2025-24016.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-24016.yaml","https://github.com/rapid7/metasploit-framework/blob/fcd24bcde44c83907fc2e965d2d0edd0cb92051b/modules/exploits/linux/http/wazuh_auth_rce_cve_2025_24016.rb","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/c82e1e98119c564b0325f2c203e3475b09c90003/data/2025/CVE-2025-24016-0xjessie21_CVE-2025-24016.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-24016/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-24016.rules","https://github.com/0xjessie21/CVE-2025-24016/blob/02118546f7a4361e8136cc5ac7079eced88fd646/CVE-2025-24016.py","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2025/CVE-2025-24016.poc","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2025-24016_1.yaml","https://github.com/0xjessie21/CVE-2025-24016","https://github.com/guinea-offensive-security/Wazuh-RCE","https://github.com/MuhammadWaseem29/CVE-2025-24016","https://github.com/huseyinstif/CVE-2025-24016-Nuclei-Template","https://github.com/rxerium/CVE-2025-24016","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-24016"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0022.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0007","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-0282","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10923,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10941}}","description":"Ivanti Connect Secure（22.7R2.5 之前版本）、Ivanti Policy Secure（22.7R1.2 之前版本）以及 Ivanti Neurons for ZTA 网关（22.7R2.3 之前版本）的 Web 组件存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞（CWE-121/CWE-787）。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标设备的受影响服务发送特制的恶意网络请求，触发栈上缓冲区溢出并覆盖返回地址，从而在目标系统上以系统权限执行任意代码，实现完全远程代码执行。该漏洞无需合法凭据、无需用户交互，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标设备的监听端口，危害等级为严重（CVSS 9.0），已被公开利用，影响大量部署上述网关的企业远程接入与零信任架构。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-0282"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-01-08T23:15:09.763","updated":"2026-06-17T08:26:12.503","remediation":"立即将 Ivanti Connect Secure 升级至 22.7R2.5 或更高版本，Ivanti Policy Secure 升级至 22.7R1.2，Ivanti Neurons for ZTA gateways 升级至 22.7R2.3。若暂无法升级，须运行 Ivanti 外部完整性检查工具 (ICT) 进行威胁狩猎，发现异常立即断网并执行工厂重置，同时重置管理员密码、API 密钥及本地用户密码，在防火墙层面限制管理接口访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://forums.ivanti.com/s/article/Security-Advisory-Ivanti-Connect-Secure-Policy-Secure-ZTA-Gateways-CVE-2025-0282-CVE-2025-0283","https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/ivanti-connect-secure-vpn-zero-day","https://www.cisa.gov/cisa-mitigation-instructions-cve-2025-0282","https://github.com/sfewer-r7/CVE-2025-0282","https://labs.watchtowr.com/exploitation-walkthrough-and-techniques-ivanti-connect-secure-rce-cve-2025-0282/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-0282","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?search_api_fulltext=CVE-2025-0282","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52213","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-0282.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-0282.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/c2672e36893bd220d6f65c955e260796d11ed64b/2025/CVE-2025-0282.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-0282.yaml","https://github.com/lal0ne/vulnerability/blob/5b9f397c1970203b1764fb7a66a0ffac39bef4cc/Ivanti/CVE-2025-0282/README.md","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/9e669818e6334d592d44717c5ec3d75ca4cc97e4/data/2025/CVE-2025-0282-44xo_CVE-2025-0282.md","https://github.com/sfewer-r7/CVE-2025-0282/blob/e1a46435a7175b9a6cee56f5a9fd4f0646e69182/CVE-2025-0282.rb","https://github.com/Threekiii/CVE/blob/b15267648d6c329465c8b4cfbeb7597850ead8c1/2025/2025.01/CVE-2025-0282%EF%BC%9AIvanti%20Connect%20Secure%20%E6%A0%88%E6%BA%A2%E5%87%BA%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-01/%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%20Ivanti%20Connect%20Secure%20RCE%20%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20%EF%BC%88CVE-2025-0282%EF%BC%89%20%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%20PoC.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-0282.rules","https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflare-docs/blob/6ca38245cd4f76ea240e519a68d43bb56ac01013/src/content/changelog/waf/2025-03-10-waf-release.mdx","https://github.com/absholi7ly/CVE-2025-0282-Ivanti-exploit","https://github.com/watchtowrlabs/CVE-2025-0282","https://github.com/Hexastrike/Ivanti-Connect-Secure-Logs-Parser","https://github.com/AnonStorks/CVE-2025-0282-Full-version","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-0282"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0062","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0062.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"明源ERP SSO登录身份认证绕过漏洞","description":"明源ERP 的 SSO 单点登录模块存在身份认证绕过漏洞，攻击者可通过向 /PubPlatform/nav/login/sso/login.aspx 接口发送特制 POST 请求，利用 __yzsAppSecret 参数及编码后的 user_info 数据绕过身份验证机制，获取有效 userToken 后直接访问系统后台。该漏洞导致未授权用户可绕过登录限制，获取 ERP 系统管理权限，造成敏感数据泄露。攻击者只需网络可达目标系统即可远程利用，无需任何认证信息，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-00642fb4"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0703","updated":"0703","remediation":"联系明源云官方获取最新安全补丁，升级 ERP 系统至修复 SSO 认证绕过漏洞的版本。临时缓解措施：在 WAF/IPS 层面配置规则，拦截对 /PubPlatform/nav/login/sso/login.aspx 路径中 __yzsAppSecret 和 user_info 参数的非授权访问请求；限制该接口仅允许可信内网 IP 访问；审查并回收所有异常 userToken 会话。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0062.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0061","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0061.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"润乾报表任意文件写入漏洞","description":"润乾报表（Runqian Report）存在任意文件写入漏洞，其文件上传或报表处理相关接口未对写入路径与文件内容进行严格校验，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过构造恶意的请求参数，将任意内容写入目标服务器的指定路径（如 Web 目录下的脚本文件）。成功利用后，攻击者可写入 JSP/WebShell 等可执行文件，从而在特定条件下实现远程代码执行（RCE）。该漏洞影响部署了存在缺陷版本润乾报表的各类应用系统，攻击条件为攻击者能够网络访问目标报表服务且相关接口对外开放，危害程度较高，建议尽快排查并升级至官方修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-005ee0ad"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0709","updated":"0709","remediation":"立即升级润乾报表至官方已修复该任意文件写入漏洞的安全版本（建议联系厂商获取 2025 年最新补丁包并升级到 V5.8 及以上版本）。临时缓解措施：在应用服务器前端部署 WAF 规则限制对报表上传/保存接口的路径遍历与非常规后缀写入，将报表文件存储目录设为只读并禁止执行权限，同时限制相关业务端口仅对内网开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0061.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0060","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0060.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"美特 CRM headimgsave SQL注入漏洞","description":"美特 CRM 的 headimgsave 接口存在 SQL 注入漏洞，攻击者通过向 accountid 参数注入恶意 SQL 语句，可利用时间盲注技术（如 SLEEP 函数）判断数据库结构并窃取敏感数据。该漏洞无需复杂权限即可远程利用，影响使用美特 CRM 系统的相关企业，可能导致用户数据泄露。建议厂商对用户输入进行参数化查询过滤以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-00580cb5"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0705","updated":"0705","remediation":"建议对 accountid 参数实施参数化查询或预编译语句，严格过滤用户输入，禁止拼接 SQL 语句。如厂商有更新版本，请立即升级至最新版；无法升级时，部署 WAF 规则拦截含 SLEEP/AND/OR 等 SQL 注入特征请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0060.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0059","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0059.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"华易 企业管理云平台 SQL 注入漏洞","description":"华易企业管理云平台存在 /home/zy 路径的SQL注入漏洞。攻击者可通过构造恶意SQL语句绕过认证机制，直接访问或操纵数据库中的敏感数据。该漏洞影响华易企业管理云平台的用户数据安全，可能导致企业敏感信息泄露、财务数据篡改和核心业务系统瘫痪。攻击者无需身份验证即可利用此漏洞，在平台认证界面或用户注册接口发送精心构造的SQL注入Payload实现目标，严重威胁平台安全稳定。漏洞修复需对输入参数进行严格验证和过滤，并采用参数化查询技术防止SQL注入攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-004c3bdf"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0702","updated":"0702","remediation":"升级到华易企业管理云平台已修复 /home/zy 接口的最新版本（向厂商获取并确认采用参数化查询），彻底消除 SQL 注入风险；如无法立即升级，可在 WAF 对该接口添加 SQL 注入拦截规则，并限制 /home/zy 仅允许已认证用户访问，同时关闭不必要的数据库错误回显作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0059.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0058","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0058.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"红海 eHR 文件读取漏洞","description":"红海eHR人力资源管理系统中存在文件读取漏洞，攻击者可通过权限绕过机制利用该漏洞读取服务器上的敏感文件（如配置文件、数据库连接信息等）。该漏洞无需登录认证即可远程触发，攻击门槛低，可能导致企业核心数据泄露。受影响版本包括红海eHR各历史版本，建议用户尽快升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-00386035"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0702","updated":"0702","remediation":"升级红海eHR至官方最新版本，在系统配置中严格限制文件读取路径白名单，禁止目录遍历（../）操作，对用户输入的文件路径参数进行过滤和校验，仅允许读取指定目录下的文件。同时配置Web应用防火墙（WAF）规则拦截路径穿越攻击载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0058.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0057","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0057.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"汉王e脸通综合管理平台任意文件读取漏洞","description":"汉王e脸通综合管理平台 `/manage/resourceUpload/imgDownload.do` 接口未对 `filePath` 参数进行有效过滤和校验，导致存在任意文件读取漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过构造恶意请求，读取服务器上任意文件（如 WEB-INF/web.xml、配置文件等），从而获取数据库凭证、系统配置等敏感信息，为后续更深层次攻击提供跳板。该漏洞影响汉王e脸通综合管理平台全版本，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-0037bdde"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0711","updated":"0711","remediation":"在 `/manage/resourceUpload/imgDownload.do` 接口中对 `filePath` 参数进行严格的路径白名单校验，禁止包含 `../`、`..\\` 等目录穿越字符，仅允许访问指定上传目录内的文件；同时实施身份认证与权限校验，确保未授权用户无法调用该接口。建议联系汉王获取官方补丁或升级至最新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0057.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0056","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0056.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"亿邮邮件网关远程代码执行漏洞","description":"亿邮邮件网关存在远程命令执行漏洞，攻击者可通过在邮件附件文件名中注入恶意命令Payload触发漏洞。该漏洞源于网关对上传文件名过滤不严，允许使用反引号执行系统命令，攻击者可在目标服务器上执行任意命令，获取服务器控制权。漏洞影响亿邮邮件网关多个版本，危害严重。建议用户尽快升级至最新版本或部署安全防护策略。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-00361c2e"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"0715","updated":"0715","remediation":"建议联系亿邮厂商获取官方补丁并升级邮件网关至最新版本；如暂无法升级，可限制 `/usr/local/eyou/gateway/ebaselib/bin/pdftotext` 文件执行权限（`chmod -x` 或移除 SUID），同时在 WAF/IPS 侧对附件文件名中含反引号、`$()` 等 shell 特殊字符的请求进行拦截作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0056.toml"}]